<ul> 
<li><a href="http://diveintopython3.org/">Dive Into Python 3</a></li> 
<li><a href="http://diveintohtml5.org/">Dive Into HTML5</a> (in progress)</li> 
<li>Various articles about HTML5 on the WHATWG blog, including
